                                                                                          What is Open Source?                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                      Collaboration  Freedom  Transparency                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                      Open source software makes source code freely available for                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                       anyone to view, modify, and distribute.                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                             It thrives on community-driven development and collaboration.

                       Core Principles                                                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                          Transparency: Publicly accessible                           Peer Review: Community quality checks                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                          Freedom: Modify & share                                     Innovation: Fast development                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                          Collaboration: Global contributions                         Flexibility: Customizable                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                          No Fees: Free to use                                        Learning: Real-world code

                      Coding only?                                                                                                                                                                                               
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                          Join GitHub discussions, Slack/Discord, mailing                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                         No! Writing documentation, testing,                          lists                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                          translation, and design also matter                                                                                                                                                   
                                                                                                                                          Ask questions politely, follow code of conduct                       
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                         You can contribute by writing tutorials or                                                                                        
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                          blogs                                                                                                                                                                                 
                                                                                                                                          Learn from others pull requests                                     
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                                    
                         Even spreading awareness counts as contribution
